UPDATE companies SET agent_ids_notes = 'Notes:: Surfacing [Navanc](https://www.navanc.com/about-us), they''re building a tool for property evaluation which is used by lenders in collateral assessment for secured loans. Essentially replacing the local valuer model which has issues such as opacity, TAT, fraud, etc. Founder is an EO with extensive experience in the space. Early traction is also decent - ~30 lakhs MRR, cracked mid-sized NBFCs and in final stages of cracking large NBFCs. The company is raising $2-3 mn. currently. Please find [vault](https://deltazen47.sharepoint.com/:f:/s/TheVault/EoVazkQZAohMugwEJVG_hCUBzM4qFPjTsHBLgOKa2tFOEg?e=czvCd3) link, customer refs + our eval views below - <u>**Eval Views**</u> **Taha - Maybe** + EO building in domain with significant hours in the space, good set of initial clients as well- IRMA + ICICI+ NBFC (pattern match) + Depth in the space --- had clear answers on property diligence(state level), valuation ? Unsure on what this product is — BRE, AI assisted workflow, services with a CRM ? End Scale outcome-- can he expand into legal workflows as well **Dhairen – Maybe** + Domain native + Addressing a major pain point for lenders, can see a play here - need to do ref on delta in efficiency + pricing + Interesting traction - Billing 7-10 lakhs p.m. to mid scale lenders quickly ? Product v/s company? Ability to expand into adjacencies? ? There''s a large services angle at play so will need understand if there''s potential for a business with quality rev. or is it just an aggrega...' WHERE id = 294 AND (agent_ids_notes IS NULL OR agent_ids_notes = '');
